        {
            "title": "颱風樺加沙｜TVB十號波下遭外資基金再減持　套現811萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"颱風樺加沙｜TVB再遭外資基金Silchester減持，被套現811萬元。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eDdvCaputHvIB6.C0r7dOw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/am730_578/559e67da12a285e087ec6b65ef739832\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">颱風樺加沙｜TVB再遭外資基金Silchester減持，被套現811萬元。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">超強颱風「樺加沙」本周三(24日)襲港，天文台發出十號風球，但在「打風不停市」下，港股市場依舊運作。根據聯交所最新權益披露，英國基金公司Silchester當日無懼惡劣天氣，繼續減持電視廣播(TVB，511)的股份。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當日Silchester一共減持234.69萬股或0.51%，平均每股作價3.4588元，套現約811.75萬元。完成減持後，該基金於TVB的持股量下降至2,756.42萬股或5.9%。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7e9b0d38-bc45-3021-8b24-f1966bf44714-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今次並非Silchester近期首次減持TVB。對上一次權益披露顯示，該基金於8月22日亦曾出售TVB的20.73萬股，每股平均價為4.1271元，套現約85.55萬元，<span><span><span><span><span>持股量降至3,247.3萬股或6.95%，以及在8月6日，亦曾減持TVB的股價。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>截至發稿，TVB股價午後微升0.01元，報3.41元，成交額87.27億元。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/颱風樺加沙-tvb十號波下遭外資基金再減持-套現811萬元/603321?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/颱風樺加沙-tvb十號波下遭外資基金再減持-套現811萬元/603321?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/颱風樺加沙-tvb十號波下遭外資基金再減持-套現811萬元/603321?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E6%A8%BA%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%99-tvb%E5%8D%81%E8%99%9F%E6%B3%A2%E4%B8%8B%E9%81%AD%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E5%86%8D%E6%B8%9B%E6%8C%81-%E5%A5%97%E7%8F%BE811%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-052243036.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-26 13:35:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "韓國銀行業罷工呼籲實行每周四天半工作制 稱可緩解倦怠、提高生育率",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"725\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dVY1Zl0_6pn7x8gEyZ8eCw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyNTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/81d020ae7a4cded2b6e1024d3de5d6b8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 數以千計的韓國銀行員工參加大罷工，並在首爾市中心舉行集會，要求獲得更高工資並縮短每周工時。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據當地媒體報導，實際參與人數不及韓國金融業工會預估的8萬人，因一些私人銀行的工會組織選擇不加入罷工。參加罷工的銀行員工尋求得到5%的加薪，並引入每周工作四天半工作制。韓國目前實行五天工作制，每周最多工作40小時、加班12小時。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"9月26日，首爾的罷工參與者，罷工由韓國金融業工會組織。攝影師：SeongJoon Cho/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mh9RLvybljz_XHEnCdWS3w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ad917b6abe4a8cf2b7a58aefc39f363b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">9月26日，首爾的罷工參與者，罷工由韓國金融業工會組織。攝影師：SeongJoon Cho/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金融業工會高級副主席Kim Jin Hong向彭博表示：「管理層知道，減少工作時間不會損害銀行業。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5244bd2d-cdeb-3329-bdde-126abe221fd7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">長期以來，韓國以馬拉松式的辦公時長和企業高壓文化而著稱。工會領導人認為，縮短每周工作時間對於緩解員工倦怠和扭轉國家生育率下降趨勢至關重要。韓國每名婦女生育0.75個孩子，生育率為世界最低。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"725\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5j_cHB5xE2fB8LujjOLyyg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyNTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/872e94a728995555c28603db364fb8d8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題South Korean Bank Staff Strike Demanding Shorter Work Week (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Shinhye Kang、Anshuman Daga.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%AF%A6%E8%A1%8C%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A9%E5%8D%8A%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%88%B6-%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E7%B7%A9%E8%A7%A3%E5%80%A6%E6%80%A0-%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E7%94%9F%E8%82%B2%E7%8E%87-041258076.html",
